Etabawua Esra Yerusalem


1  Ore apa te siadi ena, te nkitoria e Artaseses olaiguanani le Parsia, ore Esra olayioni le Seraia, olayioni le Asaria, olayioni le Hilkia, 
2  olayioni le Shalum, olayioni le Sadok, olayioni le Ahitab, 
3  olayioni le Amaria, olayioni le Asaria, olayioni le Merariot, 
4  olayioni le Serahia, olayioni le Usii, olayioni le Buki, 
5  olayioni le Abishua, olayioni le Finehas, olayioni le Eliesa, olayioni le Aron ilo apolosani kitok - neilepu sii ilo Esra eing'uaa Babilon. 
6  Olaigeroni apa ninye arriyia too nkitanapat e Musa, apa naaishorua Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel, neisho olaiguanani ninye nena pooki naatoomonuo, amu etii apa enkaina o Laitoriani Enkai enye shumata ninye.


7  Neilep sii apa aapuo Yerusalem to lapa liopishana le nkitoria e Artaseses olaiguanani, embata oo ltung'ana loo Siraeli, o embata oo lapolosak o Lawi, o laranyak o larripok loo nchomito, o laisiaayiak le nkaji e Nkai. 
8  Nelotu ninye Yerusalem to lapa le imiet, aa olari liopishana le nkitoria eilo aiguanani; 
9  amu ore te nkolong e dukuya o lapa le dukuya neiteru ninye alo te Babilon, ore te nkolong e dukuya o lapa le imiet nelotu ninye Yerusalem, amu etii enkaina supat e Nkai enye shumata ninye. 
10  Amu etipika Esra oltau lenye pee eiteng'enuo enkitanapata o Laitoriani, neas ninye, neitengenisho nkiguanat enyena, o nkikoo enyena tiatua Israel.

Mbaa naaigeroki naaishoo Artaseses Esra


11  Ena entashati e mpalai naishoo olaiguanani Artaseses Esra ilo apolosani, naa olaigeroni, ang'eni loo mbaa oo nkitanapat o Laitoriani o nkiguanat enyena tialo Isiraeli: 
12  “Artaseses olaiguanani loo laiguanak oirriwaki Esra olapolosani, ilo aigeroni loo nkitanapat e Nkai e keper. Ore taata, 
13  aitobira nanu enkitanapata ore pooki ng'ae too ltung'ana loo Siraeli anaa ilapolosak lenye anaa Ilawi tiatua enkitoria ai, onyorraa alo Yerusalem te yieunoto enye, neidim ashomo tenebo iyie. 
14  Amu kirriwayie iyie olaiguanani o lautarok lenyena oopishana, pee eikilikuan mbaa e Yuda o Yerusalem te risioroto eina kitanapata natii nkaik inono, e Nkai ino, 
15  nimbalunye sii enkosholai o sahabu apa naishoo olaiguanani tenebo ilautarok Enkai e Israel, natii emanyisho enye atua Yerusalem, 
16  tenebo enkosholai pooki o sahabu nilo iyie atum to lkerenket pooki le Babilon, tenebo nkishorot o lpela oo ltung'ana o noo lapolosak, naainosaki olmumai pee eishoruni tenkaraki enkaji e Nkai enye natii Yerusalem. 
17  Ore naa te kuna pisai ilo iyie ainyiang'u iloing'ok, o lmeregeshi, o lkuo le kerra, tenebo ilasarri lenye le ntapa, o lasarri lenye ooki, nilo aishooyo ninche te nchumata olperere lo lasar le nkaji e Nkai ino natii Yerusalem. 
18  Ore pooki naba anaa enidol aa sidai te iyie o lalashera linono neasi teina ae osholai o sahabu, nindimidimi aataas, te risioroto e yieunoto e Nkai ino. 
19  Ore inapa masaa nikinchooki tenkaraki enkisiaayiare e nkaji e Nkai ino, nilo aitayu te dukuya e Nkai e Yerusalem. 
20  Ore pooki naba anaa enayieuni te nkaraki enkaji e Nkai ino, niata erishata pee inchoru nindim aishoru te nena naatii olchumati lo laiguanani.


21  “Ore nanu Artaseses olaiguanani, naitobira enkitanapata too lashumak pooki lo lkerenket otii teidia alo olkeju. Ore pooki nayieu Esra, ilo apolosani, aigeroni loo nkitanapat e Nkai e keper, nchoo easi aakurraki, 
22  neitabaikini ntalantani iip nabo e nkosholai, o rridat iip e nkano, o lbenia iip le nkano, o emunyan neitu eimakini eneba esapuko. 
23  Ore pooki naaitanapishe Enkai e keper, nchoo metaasi aaitabaya te nkaraki enkaji e Nkai e keper, pee melotu ake engoro enye adoiki olaiguanani o layiok lenyena. 
24  Kiliki sii iyie nchere meishiaakino pee eitalaki olapolosani kodi e arakinoto, anaa mpisai o lpolosie, anaa mpisai e nkoitoi, nemeitalaki Ilawi o laranyak, o laitasheikinok loo nkutukie oo nkajijik, o laisiaayiak le nkaji e Nkai, anaa kulikae aisiaayiak le nkaji e Nkai.


25  “Naa ore iyie Esra te risioroto eina ng'eno nagut e Nkai ino niata te nkaina ino, tegelu ilooiguanare o larishak oorish iltung'ana to lkerenket pooki otii lido kekun olkeju, ore lelo pooki naa ilooyiolo nkitanapat Enkai ino: ore lelo lemeyiolo nkitanapat ninteng'en. 
26  Ore pooki ng'ae lemeiruk nkitanapat e Nkai ino o nkitanapat o laiguanani, nchoo edung'okini ninye enkiguana narrish, aa te keeya, anaa erewe eyararoto anaa, eoruni imasaa enyena, anaa eeni te korokoroni.”

Eisisa Esra Enkai


27  Meisisi Olaitoriani, Enkai oo loo papa, laa ninye otipika embae naikununo nji atua oltau lo laiguanani, pee eitisidan enkaji e Nkai natii Yerusalem, 
28  naa ninye laaitabaikia nanu enyorrata enye nauno te dukuya olaiguanani, o lautarok lenyena. O te dukuya iltung'ana pooki magil lo laiguanani. Naagolu nanu oshoke amu etii enkaina o Laitoriani Enkai ai shumata nanu, naiturrur nanu iltung'ana ooisul Isiraeli pee aapuo aairiamariyie.

